sources.description:
Man Bait! She Spelled Trouble For Every Guy That Made A Play For Her! 
When beautiful Mary returns home to her "whistle stop" home town, long-standing feelings of animosity between two of her old boyfriends leads to robbery and murder.

Original title: Whistle Stop (1946)


Black & White version: https://youtu.be/N72UHE7V94A


Director: Léonide Moguy 
Writers: Maritta M. Wolff, Philip Yordan 
Stars: George Raft, Ava Gardner, Victor McLaglen, Tom Conway
Genres: Colorized, Crime, Drama, Film-Noir 

This film has subtitles in many languages.


00:00 Full Movie (with subtitles).
02:37 Mary returns to Ashbury and reconnects with Molly and Kenny.
13:30 Fran returns to town and confronts Lew Lentz about their past.
16:51 A man named Kenny is being threatened by someone at a private party.
35:38 Mary's family is upset with Kenny for drinking and not working at the fair.
50:02 Fran is terminally ill and Kenny is by her side, expressing his love and support.
58:47 Mary's wedding is interrupted when Gitlo and X arrive, and they are chased by unknown individuals.
1:09:52 Kenny is in trouble after being wrongly accused of a robbery, and his friends are determined to clear his name.
